<br>
Thats not too bad.<br>
<br>
Also for these unprepped melees you can leave a party and log for the night after giving them the amulet and component.   The night doesnt' have to end there.<br>
<br>
So yeah it's definitly limited use, but it's not useless.<br>
<br>
As for eye of tallon.. The only thing not useful about it, is the fact it turns you invisible and kills your pet.  Other than that it lasts longer, sees invis, and seems to even move faster than eye of zomm.   I use this spell a lot to scout.  Even summon the mantle so it lasts a bit longer.<br>
<br>
